Multi-tubule conduit-filler constructs loaded with gradient-distributed growth 
factors for neural tissue engineering applications.

Wu H(1), Fang Q(2), Liu J(2), Yu X(2), Xu Y(3), Wan Y(4), Xiao B(5).

Author information:
(1)Department of Nuclear Medicine and Minnan PET Center, the First Affiliated 
Hospital of Xiamen University, Xiamen 316003, PR China.
